==English==

===Noun===
'''doom'''
#An impending severe problem that seems inevitable.
#A feeling of danger, impending danger, darkness or dispair.
#A popular first person shooter, involving demons on Phobos, that has spawned multiple sequels.  A historic game in that it was one of the first pseudo-3D first person shooters, and is looked upon by many to be the metaphorical father of the genre.  Locations in the original and sequals included Phobos, hell, and Mars respectively.

